y-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/dragstart_event\"><code>dragstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/drop_event\"><code>drop</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><em><code>input</code></em></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/mscandidatewindowhide_event\"><code>mscandidatewindowhide</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/mscandidatewindowshow_event\"><code>mscandidatewindowshow</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/mscandidatewindowupdate_event\"><code>mscandidatewindowupdate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/paste_event\"><code>paste</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herencia</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>El evento <strong><code>input</code></strong> se dispara cuando el valor (<code>value</code>) de un elemento <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code></a>, o <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a> ha sido cambiado. </p>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Burbujas</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Cancelable</th>\n   <td>No</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Interfaz</th>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/InputEvent\"><code>InputEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Objectivo</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Acción por defecto</th>\n   <td>None</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Propiedad del manejador del evento</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/es/docs/conflicting/Web/API/HTMLElement/input_event\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers.oninput</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>El evento también aplica a los elementos con la propiedad <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/contentEditable\" title=\"contenteditable\"><code>contenteditable</code></a> habilidado, y para cualquier otro elemento cuando la propiedad <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Document/designMode\" title=\"designMode\"><code>designMode</code></a> esta encendida. En el caso de un <code>contenteditable</code> y <code>designMode</code>, el objetivo del evento es el  the event target is the <em>editing host</em>. Si estas propiedades aplian a múltiples elementos, el host de edición es el elemento ancestro más cercano cuyo padre no es editable.</p>\n\n<p>Para elementos <code>&lt;input&gt;</code> con <code>type=checkbox</code> o <code>type=radio</code>, el evento <code>input</code> debería disparar cuando el usuario alterna el control, por <a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/input.html#the-input-element:event-input-2\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">la especificación HTML5</a>. Sin embargo, históricamente no siempre es el caso. Revise la compatibilidad o use el evento <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/change_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">change (en-US)</a></code> en su lugar para estos tipos.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>Nota:</strong> A diferencia de <code>input</code>, el evento <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/change_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">change (en-US)</a></code> no es disparado necesariamente por cada alteración al valor (<code>value</code>) de un elemento.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ejemplos","title":"Ejemplos","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Este ejemplo registra el valor siempre que se cambia el valor del elemento <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">placeholder</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Ingrese algún texto<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>nombre<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>valores<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"javascript","title":"JavaScript","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> input <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'input'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> log <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'valores'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\ninput<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'input'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> updateValue<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">updateValue</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  log<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>srcElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"resultado","title":"Resultado","isH3":true,"content":"<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Ejemplos\" id=\"frame_examples\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/es/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/input_event/_sample_.examples.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>\n\n<p>(Funciona en la versión en inglés)</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificaciones","title":"Especificaciones","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificación</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Estado</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/forms.html#event-input-input\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"es\">La definición de 'input event' en esta especificación.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/2014/WD-DOM-Level-3-Events-20140925/#event-type-input\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 3 Events Specification<br><small lang=\"es\">La definición de 'input event' en esta especificación.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsolete</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidad de los navegadores","id":"compatibilidad_de_los_navegadores","isH3":false,"data":null,"query":"api.HTMLElement.input","browsers":null}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":